text: They took our body measurements to so call make a fresh piece of baju kurung but instead when we collect the baju kurung, there were sizing labels on the shirt, it indicates that they buy off from someone and sell it to us. And some of the baju is not even up to our bosy measurements. Thank you .

Went to this boutique today. Very disappointed because none of them approached or served us. When we asked for help, they looked at each other as if signaling…‘who’s going to serve her?’ We asked for a size for men’s baju kurung, was told by one of them that she will look for the size but nothing, we stood there waiting but nothing came. Had purchased from this shop a couple of times, but I guess not again.
